		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;384px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最后的效果，主菜单中也只有退出按钮了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://evine.win/p/kodi-disable-shutdown/pic5.png&#34;
